{"tid":1640884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整左個虛擬連儂牆俾外國朋友access","createTime":"2019-10-09T07:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T16:52:49.000Z","uid":45683,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2915677b27fa075936103efe3b66d6af95dc3c96","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AypaQqE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAypaQqE.png&h=ac97e248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://padlet.com/letssavehk/jj6hg36493a9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpadlet.com%2Fletssavehk%2Fjj6hg36493a9&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=95e66b51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://padlet.com/letssavehk/jj6hg36493a9</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTarget： <br />\n1）俾有興趣知道發生咩事嘅人一次過睇到哂發生過咩事同大家點諗<br />\n2）俾個途徑佢地show support<br />\n<br />\n大家可以自由上去post文宣, 俾like, 然後我地推上twitter俾外國人留言, 有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"6826901843ae5300337c5070074fc76454c724f3","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bce2cfcf415678a75409e6bc73832b08b2e1651e","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"0e35854e69e5be616415546c506d163060838cca","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5fe6b7a8f2f167ad33405b60f2ca77187d8f6100","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:10:29.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c941e73044bf34d765d19ab520789981825ffde5","tid":1640884,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf4cdde1a9ff838821791db691268f36ba13265","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0cc6a4c978a09b31afc3e2269ef159124acc204f","tid":1640884,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016657d51f1b9e54155ce39a7be153b6c21e8c07","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"3a9209aac46e40f6566483bd91d4f0a6c5fb0f44","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:12:34.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"7227dcdb46b1c64c5f59806941abb29870373f28","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"8e4a24f34b217bcb77d96c0fce1bc4923ec8bd85","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"745efebf324de42fda18ce5f0de88c029ce37f9e","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:13:13.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"ef930025f8eb18bf032df3ee29da866150938a27","tid":1640884,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"推上twitter<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"bea3e5a14eab2b0fc78cd96fec24addfc660e5f9","tid":1640884,"uid":94402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"右下果位巴, 我都有集佢郵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afed81c3584f76bd6792a1d2842617d8c39774c1","tid":1640884,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"不如我地幫佢地實體化"},{"pid":"939b89bc0bea034e0d2a600dbd049a6e8a714dab","tid":1640884,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"1bc477947c1824cab763604c90d351098a220472","tid":1640884,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afea799b1d4c6f7c7bd4c196a703e341a7b316b8","tid":1640884,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afed81c3584f76bd6792a1d2842617d8c39774c1","tid":1640884,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"不如我地幫佢地實體化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"如果有外國朋友post野， 我唔介意幫佢印出嚟黐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82593f8bdb8028d8b57d5ed701ee2532a4ff22d5","tid":1640884,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:32:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c99eb725e3135e9803118eef475df2ba913bf1c","tid":1640884,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:34:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c0f4645e2e5c27aa9d772dfe12e732855e09aca1","tid":1640884,"uid":65089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r